data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. A LARGE GUEST SUITE WITH INDEPENDENT ENTRANCE WITH STREET FRONT, MUCH SPACE, GOOD LOCATION, A LARGE PATIO AND A GREAT DRIVEWAY ARE SOME OF THE BENEFITS YOU WILL GET WHEN PURCHASING THIS HOME!!!... the Guest Suite YOU CAN RENT IT, or you could use it to have your mother, your mother-in-law or some family member with you but independent and with privacy!!! You can access it externally or internally from the Main House. It includes a Portal, Living Room, Dining Room-Kitchen, a spacious Bedroom with closet and a full Bathroom.    The Main House has an independent entrance also to the Portal (with a different facade, decorated with four monumental sculptures), Living Room, Kitchen-Dining Room, Family Room, two Bedrooms with closets and two full Bathrooms. A large Patio around the property, in front a big circular Driveway, carport for 2 cars, the house has its entire perimeter fenced: Metal Fence in front and Vinyl Fence in the backyard, with an entrance for large vehicles. NEW ROOF from 2022, Central Air from 2019 (4 tons), New Water Heater from 2022, Electrical Panel from 2017, Public Water, Public Sewer and Utilities.    This House is conveniently close to the center of Punta Gorda, and the center of Port Charlotte, just 2 blocks from the main avenue Highway 41, near the I-75 Expressway, surrounded by a wide variety of Shops, Restaurants, good Schools, Parks, Hospitals and Healthcare Facilities, entertainment options such as top-notch fishing opportunities being just minutes from Charlotte Harbor, very close to the New Sunseeker Resort Charlotte Harbor..... and much more!!!!
